You can sign up for daily or nightly
patrols, which might seem like overkill,

54
00:04:01,341 --> 00:04:06,176
but regular surveillance will deter
even the most determined criminal.

55
00:04:06,246 --> 00:04:12,185
Are there any other questions?
All right. Let's be careful out there.

56
00:04:14,754 --> 00:04:17,951
- Actually, do you have a second?
- Sure. How can I help?

57
00:04:18,024 --> 00:04:20,652
Um... I'm the one
who discovered the break-in.

58
00:04:20,760 --> 00:04:23,388
- I think I found some evidence.
- Evidence?

59
00:04:23,463 --> 00:04:28,526
This is a screwdriver left behind
by the burglar. I didn't touch it.

60
00:04:28,635 --> 00:04:31,468
Why didn't you give this
to the investigators?

61
00:04:31,571 --> 00:04:33,630
I tried and they laughed at me.

62
00:04:33,706 --> 00:04:35,833
Nothing was taken from the house.

63
00:04:35,942 --> 00:04:38,911
I apologize.
That was totally unprofessional.

64
00:04:38,978 --> 00:04:43,074
Thank you. So you think
it should be dusted for prints?

65
00:04:43,149 --> 00:04:46,949
- Yes. And I'll make sure it gets done.
- Great.

66
00:04:49,522 --> 00:04:51,490
Bye.

67
00:04:56,796 --> 00:04:59,492
Boys, stop it! Go to bed!

68
00:04:59,565 --> 00:05:02,796
- We're not tired!
- Well, at least go upstairs.

69
00:05:02,869 --> 00:05:05,736
- We want to play!
- Look!

70
00:05:07,073 --> 00:05:09,564
Gimme!

71
00:05:09,676 --> 00:05:11,405
Go! Go!

72
00:05:12,378 --> 00:05:14,437
