73
00:05:16,482 --> 00:05:20,043
So why weren't you sitting with Mike?
I thought you two were an item.

74
00:05:20,119 --> 00:05:23,179
I sort of thought so too.
Getting a lot of mixed signals.

75
00:05:23,256 --> 00:05:27,158
I'll tell you who wasn't giving mixed
signals. Sexy Officer Thompson.

76
00:05:27,226 --> 00:05:29,888
- He stared at you all night.
- You noticed that?

77
00:05:29,962 --> 00:05:33,193
Honey, trust me, when
they're not staring at me, I notice.

78
00:05:33,299 --> 00:05:35,961
I appreciate you guys
staying and helping.

79
00:05:36,035 --> 00:05:38,196
Oh, please.
I would have hosted it myself

80
00:05:38,304 --> 00:05:41,603
but there's camping equipment
everywhere.

81
00:05:41,674 --> 00:05:43,733
It's nice of you.

82
00:05:43,810 --> 00:05:46,836
And there's something else nice
that I'd like you to do.

83
00:05:46,913 --> 00:05:49,905
Your kids both went to
Barcliff Academy, didn't they?

84
00:05:50,016 --> 00:05:54,385
